metadata.description: AMAZING SPIDER-MAN: EXTRA! takes a deeper glimpse into Spidey's world with three stories that flesh out his family, friends and foes. Spidey Braintrust members Guggenheim and Wells welcome Joe Kelly for a story marking the return of one of Peter's most unforgettable enemies: Hammerhead!
metadata.name: Amazing Spider-Man: Extra! , Vol. 1
